                <h2>Space</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-text">
                <p class="info-sentence">NuLA-10n represents a colossal gas giant, potentially ranking among the largest planetary bodies ever catalogued in our cosmic surveys.</p>
                <p class="info-sentence">This magnificent celestial body exhibits a predominantly helium and hydrogen atmospheric composition, characteristic of massive gaseous worlds.</p>
                <p class="info-sentence">Located approximately 847 light-years from Earth, NuLA-10n challenges our understanding of planetary formation and evolution.</p>
            </div>
